quran[564]{c,v,t}:
  78,1,Kungantoni na oko baphikisana ngako
  78,2,KungeeNdaba ezinkulu
  78,3,Ezo bangenakuvumelana ngazo
  78,4,"Yeha, inene kungekudala baza kwazi"
  78,5,"Kwakhona yeha, inene kungekudala baza kwazi"
  78,6,"ASiwenzanga\tumhlaba\twaba\tngumphangalalo owandlalekileyo na"
  78,7,Neentaba1 zaba zizikhonkwane
  78,8,Saza Sanidala ngambini
  78,9,Senza ukulala kwenu (kwaba lixesha) lokuphumla
  78,10,Senza ubusuku isigqumathelo
  78,11,Senza imini ixesha lokuxelengela ukuphila
  78,12,Sakha phezu kwenu amazulu asixhenxe omeleleyo
  78,13,Sabeka apho isibane esikhazimlayo
  78,14,Sathoba amanzi ngobuninzi emafini emvula
  78,15,Ukuze ngawo Sivelise imbewu nezityalo
  78,16,Nemiyezo eshinyeneyo
  78,17,Inene iMini yohlenga-hlengiso yinto esele imiselwe kakade
  78,18,"Mini leyo, iXilongo liya kuvuthelwa nize nibuyiswe niziindimbane"
  78,19,Namazulu avuleke ngokungathi ziingcango
  78,20,Neentaba zithi shwaka ngokungathi yinkohliso
  78,21,Inene isiHogo sihleli sincathamile
  78,22,Likhaya lokuhlala abo bangabagabadeli (abenzi bezono)
  78,23,Baya kuhlala apho kuso iminyaka ngeminyaka
  78,24,"Akukho nto ipholileyo baya kukuyingcamla apho, kungekho nasiselo na kakade"
  78,25,"Ngaphandle kolwelo3 olubilayo, nobubomvu"
  78,26,Umvuzo ofanelekileyo (waboni)
  78,27,Kuba abazanga boyike kufakwa ngxoxweni (ngezenzo zabo)
  78,28,Basuka bathabatha imiqondiso yeThu njengobuxoki
  78,29,Kwaye yonke into Siyigcinile eNcwadini
  78,30,"(Kuya kuthiwa kubo): “Ngcamlani ke iziqhamo (zezenzo zenu) kuba akukho songezelelo eSiya kuninika sona ngaphandle kwesohlwayo!”"
  78,31,"Inene, kumalungisa iya kuba yimpumelelo"
  78,32,"IMiyezo ebiyelweyo, nemidiliya"
  78,33,neentombi ezibudala bulinganayo
  78,34,Nendebe ezele qhu
  78,35,Akukho mampunge baya kuwava apho nabuxoki
  78,36,Umvuzo ophuma eNkosini yakho. Isipho esaneleyo
  78,37,"INkosi yamazulu nomhlaba, nako konke okuphakathi kuwo, uSolubabalo; Akukho namnye oya kuba nagunya lakuthetha naYe"
  78,38,"IMini apho uMoya (oyiNgcwele) neengelosi ziya kuma ngemigca. Akukho namnye oya kuthetha ngaphandle kwalowo uya kuvunyelwa nguSozinceba, yaye uya kuthetha okulungileyo kuphela"
  78,39,"Leyo\tyiMini\tyeNyaniso!\tNgako\toko\tlowo\tufunayo makathabathe ukhuseleko ngeNkosi yakhe"
  78,40,"Inene Sinilumkisile ngesohlwayo esikufuphi. Mini leyo umntu aya kuzibona izenzo zezandla zakhe, aze athi umchasi- kholo: “Yeha kum! Akwaba bendiluthuli"
  79,1,"Ndifunga\tngezo\t(ngelosi)\tzirhola\t(imiphefumlo yabangcolileyo), ngokurhabaxa"
  79,2,Nangezo zirhola (imiphefumlo yamalungisa) ngocoselelo
  79,3,"Nangezo ziphaphazela, zindande (zithunywa imiyalezo yenceba)"
  79,4,Zingxamele phambili ngokungathi ziselugqatsweni
  79,5,Zide zicwangcise (imiyalelo yeNkosi yazo) (xa kukhala iXilongo)
  79,6,"NgeMini\tukuvuthelwa\t(kweXilongo\tlokuqala)\tkuya kudlokovisa (indalo)"
  79,7,Kulandele intshukumo emva kwentshukumo (xa kukhala elesibini)
  79,8,Iintliziyo ziya kubetha kabuhlungu ngaloo Mini
  79,9,Amehlo abe buthathaka (ondele phantsi)
  79,10,"Bathi: “Ingaba ngenene siza kubuyiselwa kwimo yethu yamandulo na"
  79,11,Nokuba sele singamathambo abolileyo?”
  79,12,"Bathi: “Okokuba kunjalo, kuya kuba kukubuya okunelahleko (oko).”"
  79,13,"Inene, iya kuba sisikhalo esinye (seXilongo)"
  79,14,"Yabonani, baya kutyekezelwa ngaphandle (kwamangcwaba abo)"
  79,15,Ingaba sele lifikile na ibali likaMûsâ kuwe
  79,16,"Xa\tiNkosi\tyakhe Yaye Yambiza\tkwintili\t(engcwele) yaseTuwâ"
  79,17,"(Yathi kuye): “Yiya kuFir’awn kuba sele egabadele!”"
  79,18,"Uthi kuye: “Akungethandi na ukuhlambuluka ezonweni"
  79,19,Nokuba ndikukhokelele eNkosini yakho ukuze uYoyike?”
  79,20,Ngoko (UMûsâ) wambonisa umqondiso omkhulu
  79,21,"Kodwa uFir’awn akawamkela umqondiso, akasithobela nesikhokelo"
  79,22,"Emvakokowatshikila,wafulathelawazabalaza(ngokuchasene nomyalezo kaMûsâ)"
  79,23,"Wahlanganisa abantu bakhe, wenza isimemezo"
  79,24,"Wathi: “Mna ndiyinkosi yenu ephezulu”"
  79,25,"Kodwa uAllâh Wamhlasela, Wenza umzekelo ngaye kobu bomi nakuBomi oBuzayo"
  79,26,Inene kule mbali kukho isifundo sakhe nabani na omoyikayo uAllâh
  79,27,Kunzima na ukudala nina kunezulu eliphezulu Alakhileyo
  79,28,"Uluphakamisile uphahla lwalo, Walicwangcisa, Walinika imfezeko"
  79,29,Ugqume ubusuku balo ngobumnyama Wavelisa imini yalo ngokukhanya
  79,30,Emva koko Wandlala umhlaba
  79,31,Waza apho kuwoWavelisa amanzi wawo nedlelo lawo
  79,32,Ukanti iintaba zona Uzigxumeke zaqina nkqi
  79,33,(Ukuze apho kuphume) isixhaso senu nemfuyo yenu
  79,34,Ke kaloku kwakufika intlekele enkulu
  79,35,Mini leyo umntu aza kuyikhumbula into abe eyizabalazela
  79,36,Ukanti uMlilo wesiHogo uya kubonakaliswa uthi thaa (kumntu wonke) obonayo
  79,37,Ke lowo ungumgabadeli (umenzi wobubi)
  79,38,Owakhetha ubomi beli hlabathi (elandela iminqweno yakhe kunentando ka-Allâh)
  79,39,Inene ikhaya lakhe liya kuba nguMlilo wesiHogo
  79,40,"Kodwa yena lowo waye waba noloyiko lokumiswa phambi kweNkosi yakhe (uAllâh), wazoyisa ekulandeleni iinkanuko zakhe ezikukungcola"
  79,41,Inene iPaladesi iya kuba likhaya lakhe
  79,42,"Wena (Muhammad) bakubuza ngeYure (bathi): liya kuba nini na ilixa (lokuzalisekiswa) kwayo"
  79,43,Ayiloxanduva lwakho ukuzalisekiswa kwayo
  79,44,Inzaliseko yayo ixhomekeke eNkosini yakho
  79,45,Inene wena unguMlumkisi kulowo uyoyikayo
  79,46,Mhla bayibona (iya kuba ngathi) baphile (kulo mhlaba) injikalanga yayo okanye intsasa yayo (kuphela)
  80,1,"(UMprofeti) Wafing’iintshiya, wafulathela"
  80,2,Kuba kweza kuye indoda eyimfama
  80,3,Kodwa yintoni na enokukuchazela okokuba ngebhaqo nayo ibinokufumana ukuhlambuluka
  80,4,okanye yamkele ululeko nenkumbuzo ukuze ibe luncedo kuyo
  80,5,Hayi lowo uzicingela ukuba akaxhomekanga (kuAllâh)
  80,6,Wena usuka uhoye yena
  80,7,Nangona ingeloxanduva lwakho ukumhlambulula
  80,8,Kodwa yena lowo uze kuwe ebaleka
  80,9,Enoloyiko (lwesohlwayo sika-Allâh entliziyweni yakhe)
  80,10,Awumnanzanga yena
  80,11,Nakanye! Kuba ngenene lo nguMyalezo oyinkumbuzo
  80,12,Ngoko ke othandayo makahlale ewukhumbula
  80,13,"UseziNcwadini ezibekekileyo, eziphethwe ngentlonipheko enkulu"
  80,14,"Ziphakamile (ngesidima, zigcinwe) ngcwele"
  80,15,"Ubhalwe ngezandla zabaBhali, (iingelosi)"
  80,16,"Abahloniphekileyo, abazithobileyo benobulungisa"
  80,17,Uqalekisiwe umtu ongakholwayo! (Kungani na ukuba angabi nambulelo kuAllâh)
  80,18,Yintoni kanti (uAllâh) Amdale ngayo
  80,19,"(Umdale)\tngeqabaza\tlembewu\tyomntu!\tWamdala wazaWamlinganisela ngokwemfanelo"
  80,20,Waphinda Wamenzela lula indlela yakhe (yokuba azalwe)
  80,21,"Waphinda kwakhona Wamenza ukuba afe, angcwatywe"
  80,22,"Kwakhona ngokwentando yaKhe, Uya kumbuyisela ebomini"
  80,23,Inene umntu akakwenzanga oko Amyalele kona
  80,24,Ngoko ke umntu makakhe aqwalasele ukutya kwakhe
  80,25,Sithulula amanzi (emvula) ngobuninzi
  80,26,Size Siqhekeze umhlaba ube ngamasuntswana
  80,27,Senze iinkozo (zembewu) zihlume (izithombo) kuwo
  80,28,Imidiliya nefula (yokutyiwa yimfuyo)
  80,29,Neminquma namasundu
  80,30,NeMiyezo enemithi eshinyeneyo
  80,31,Neziqhamo namadlelo
  80,32,(Ukuba zibe) sisixhaso senu nemfuyo yenu
  80,33,Kodwa yakufika ingxolo (ukukhala kweXilongo okwesibini ngeMini yoVuko)
  80,34,Ngaloo Mini umntu uya kubaleka ashiye umntakwabo
  80,35,Nomama wakhe notata wakhe
  80,36,Nomfazi wakhe nabantwana bakhe
  80,37,"Ngaloo Mini umntu ngamnye uya kuxakeka zezakhe, angazihoyi ezabanye"
  80,38,Ngaloo Mini ubuso babanye buya kukhazimla (bube buhle)
  80,39,"Behleka, bevuyiswa ziindaba ezimnandi"
  80,40,Ubuso babanye ngaloo Mini buya kuzala luthuli bumbatshe
  80,41,Bugqunywe bubumnyama
  80,42,"Abo ngabangakholwayo, abangcolileyo, (abakrexezayo)"
  81,1,Xa ilanga lisongwa (licinywa ukukhanya)
  81,2,Naxa iinkwenkwezi zisiwa
  81,3,Naxa iintaba zenziwe zanyamalala
  81,4,Naxa iinkamela ezimithiyo zingasahoywanga
  81,5,Naxa izilo zasendle ziqokelelwe ndawonye
  81,6,Naxa iilwandle zinga zidwanguza amadangatya omlilo ziphuphuma
  81,7,Naxa imiphefumlo ihlanganiswa nemizimba yayo
  81,8,Naxa (usana) oluyintombazana olwangcwatywa luphila lubuzwa
  81,9,“Sono sini na elabulawelwa sona?”
  81,10,"Naxa\tamaphepha\t(abhaliweyo)\t[ezenzo\tezilungileyo (nezingcolileyo) zomntu ngamnye] etyhilwa elubala"
  81,11,Naxa isibhakabhaka sihlutyulwa sisuswa endaweni yaso
  81,12,Naxa uMlilo wesiHogo uphenjwa
  81,13,Naxa iPaladesi isondezelwa kufutshane
  81,14,(Ngoko) umntu ngamnye uya kuyazi into ayivelisileyo (elungileyo nengalunganga)
  81,15,Yeha! Ndifunga ngezijikelezi-langa (iiplanethi) eziphinda zihlehle
  81,16,Nangezijikelezilanga ezihamba ngokubaleka ziye kusithela
  81,17,Nangobusuku xa buphela
  81,18,Nangentseni xa ikhanya
  81,19,"Inene eli liLizwi (i’Kur’ân eliziswe) sisiThunywa esihloniphekileyo (uJibrîl, evela kuAllâh, esiza kuMprofeti uMuhammad)"
  81,20,"Esinamandla, (nobungangamsha), siphuma (kuAllâh), iNkosi yeTrone (engenakushukunyiswa yinto ngaphandle kwentando yaKhe)"
  81,21,"(UJibrîl, isithunywa) Esithotyelwayo (ziingelosi zamazulu), sikwathembekile"
  81,22,Hini na bantu! Ugxa wenu (uMuhammad) akaphambenanga
  81,23,Ngokwenene yena wambona uJibrîl elundini olucacileyo
  81,24,kwaye yena akalubandezi ulwazi (lwezinto) eziyimfihlakalo
  81,25,Ukanti (le ‘Kur’ân) ayilolizwi likaShaytân (uSathana) owaqalekiswayo
  81,26,Ngoku ke nina nisingise phi
  81,27,"Inene\tle\t(‘Kur’ân)\tayinto\tyimbi\tngaphandle\tkokuba yinkumbuzo kwindalo yonke"
  81,28,Kuye nabani na kuni ofuna ukuhamba ngokuthe tye
  81,29,"Yaye aninako ukuzithandela (ukuhamba ngokuthe tye) ngaphandle kokuba kuthande uAllâh, iNkosi yamaphakade"
  82,1,Xa isibhakabhaka sicandeka phakathi
  82,2,Naxa iinkwenkwezi zisiwa
  82,3,Naxa iilwandle ziphuphuma
  82,4,Naxa amangcwaba ebhedululiwe
  82,5,"Umphefumlo\t(ngamnye)\tuya\tkuyazi\tinto\toze\tnayo ngaphambili noyishiye ngemva"
  82,6,"Hini na wena mntu! Yintoni na ekwenze akwaYihoya iNkosi yakho, uSobubele"
  82,7,"Eyakudalayo\tYakubumba\tngemfezeko\tngomlinganiselo onguwo"
  82,8,Nayiphi na imo Ethanda ukuba ube yiyo wena; Ikudibanisa ube njalo
  82,9,Yeha inene nina niyawuphika uMgwebo
  82,10,"Inene\tphezu\tkwenu\tkukho\t(iingelosi\tezinyulelwe) ukunilondoza"
  82,11,"zilunge kakhulu, zihloniphekile, zibhala phantsi (konke) enikwenzayo"
  82,12,Zikwazi konke enikwenzayo
  82,13,Inene amalungisa aya kuba selonwabeni
  82,14,Inene abangcolileyo baya kuba seMlilweni wesiHogo
  82,15,Baya kungena kuso apho ngoMhla wemivuzo
  82,16,Yaye abasokuze bakwazi ukuphuncula kuso
  82,17,Yintoni na enokukucacisela ukuba uMhla wemivuzo (lo) uyintoni na
  82,18,"Kwakhona\tyintoni\tna\tenokukucacisela\tukuba\tuMhla wemivuzo (lo) uyintoni na"
  82,19,Iya kuba yiMini apho kungekho mphefumlo uya kuba namandla akwenzela nto omnye. Yaye ulawulo ngaloo Mini luya kuba loluka-Allâh (lonke)
  83,1,Yeha kwabo banobuqhetseba
  83,2,"Abo bathi xa kufuneka befumene into kwabanye abantu, bafune umlinganiselo ozeleyo"
  83,3,"Kodwa xa kufuneka ibe ngabo amabanike abanye abantu umlinganiselo onguwo, suke bona babanike omncinane kunofanelekileyo"
  83,4,Abacingi na ukuba baza kuphinda bavuswe (baxoxiswe)
  83,5,NgoMhla oMkhulu
  83,6,UMhla abaya kuthi bonke abantu bame phambi kweNkosi yamazwe
  83,7,"Yeha inene, imibhalo yezenzo zabangcolileyo igcinwe kwi- Sijjîn"
  83,8,Yintoni na enokukucacisela okokuba iyintoni na iSijjiîn
  83,9,YiNcwadi ebhaliweyo
  83,10,Yeha kwabo baphikayo ngaloo Mini
  83,11,Abo baphika iMini yoMgwebo
  83,12,Akakho oyiphikayo ngaphandle komoni ogabadeleyo
  83,13,"Lowo uthi xa efundelwa iziTyhilelo zeThu athi: “Ziintsomi zamandulo”"
  83,14,Nakanye! (Banongcoliseko) lomhlwa ezintliziyweni zabo ngenxa yezenzo zabo
  83,15,Inene baya kusithwa bangayiboni iNkosi yabo ngaloo Mini
  83,16,"Kwakhona, inene baya kuphoswa eMlilweni wesiHogo"
  83,17,"Yaye kuya kuthiwa (kubo): “Le yilaa (nyaniso) naniyiphika!”"
  83,18,Inene iiNcwadi zezenzo zamalungisa zigcinwe kwi- ‘Iliyyûn
  83,19,Yintoni na enokukucacisela okokuba iyintoni na i-’Iliyyûn
  83,20,YiNcwadi ebhaliweyo
  83,21,Engqinwa ngabasondele kuAllâh
  83,22,Inene amalungisa aya kuba selonwabeni
  83,23,"Ehleli ezihlalweni eziphakamileyo, emana ukujonga-jonga, (ebukela ubuhle bezinto eziseMyezweni)"
  83,24,Uya kubona inkazimlo yochulumanco ebusweni bawo
  83,25,"Unxano\tlwawo\tluya\tkuqatyulwa\tngewayini\tenyulu, etywiniweyo"
  83,26,"Etywina\tlayo\tliziziqholo\tzeMisk1:\tNantsi\tke\tinto abanomnqweno abanokukhuphisana ngayo"
  83,27,Ixutywe namanzi omthombo weTasnîm. okwabo iya kuba ngumvuzo ongasokuze ube nasiphelo
  83,28,Umthombo ekusela kuwo abo bakufuphi no Allâh
  83,29,"Inene, aboni babedla ngokubahleka abo bakholwayo"
  83,30,"Ngalo lonke ixesha begqitha ecaleni kwabo (bakholwayo), baqobelane amehlo (begculela)"
  83,31,Bathi bakufika kumawabo benze intlekisa
  83,32,"Baze bathi lonke ixesha xa bebabona bathi: “Yabonani! Aba bantu balahlekile ngenene!”"
  83,33,Ukanti babengathunywanga ukuba babe ngabalondolozi babo
  83,34,"Ngale\tMini\tngabakholwayo\tabaya\tkuba\tbehleka abangakholwayayo"
  83,35,"Behleli ezihlalweni (ezimfuma-mfuma), eziphakamileyo, bejonga-jonga"
  83,36,"Abamelanga\tkubuyekezwa\tna\tabangakholwayo\tngoko bakwenzayo"
  84,1,Xa isibhakabhaka sisahlukana phakathi
  84,2,"Siphulaphule, sithobele iNkosi yaso yaye kunyanzelekile senze njalo"
  84,3,Naxa umhlaba usanekwa
  84,4,Sele utyekezele ngaphandle konke oko bekungaphakathi kuwo
  84,5,"Uphulaphula, uthobela iNkosi yawo yaye unyanzelekile wenze njalo"
  84,6,"Hini na wena mntu! Inene, wena Uya kubuyela eNkosini yakho nezenzo zakho (oko) kukubuyela okungathandabuzekiyo"
  84,7,Lowo uya kunikwa iNcwadi yakhe (yezenzo) ngesandla sakhe sokunene
  84,8,Inene lowo kungekudala ityala lakhe liya kuxoxwa ngokulula
  84,9,Aze abuyele kwabakubo evuya
  84,10,Ke lowo uya kunikwa iNcwadi yakhe ngemva
  84,11,Uya kuthandazela ukuba atshabalale
  84,12,"Yaye uya kungena eMlilweni odwanguzayo, aviswe ukutshisa kwawo"
  84,13,Kaloku yena wayonwabile phakathi kwabakubo
  84,14,Eneneni yena wayecinga ukuba asokuze abuyele (kuThi)
  84,15,Kanti! INkosi yakhe Yayihleli Imqwalasele
  84,16,Ngoko ke Ndifunga ngokukhazimla kokutshona kwelanga
  84,17,Nangobusuku nako konke obukuqokelela ngobumnyama babo
  84,18,Nangenyanga xa ipheleleyo
  84,19,Niya kuhamba amanqanaba ngamanqanaba (kobu bomi nakuBomi oBuzayo)
  84,20,Kanti yintoni na ngabo ukuba bangakholwa
  84,21,Ukanti naxa i’Kurân icengcelezwa kubo abawi baqubude
  84,22,"Yeha\tabo\tbangakholwayo\tbayamphikisa\t(uMprofeti uMuhammad)"
  84,23,"Kanti\tYena\tuAllâh\tUkwazi\tkakuhle\tabakuqokelelayo (okuzizenzo ezilungileyo nezingcolileyo)"
  84,24,Vakalisa ke ngoko isohlwayo esibuhlungu kubo
  84,25,Ngaphandle kwabo bakholwayo benze izenzo zobulungisa
  85,1,Ndifunga ngesibhakabhaka esibambe iinkwenkwezi ezinkulu
  85,2,NangeMini yesithembiso
  85,3,NangeMini yokungqina nangeMini1 engqinelwayo
  85,4,Baqalekisiwe abenza umsele
  85,5,Womlilo ogalelwe isivuthisi
  85,6,Behleli ecaleni kwawo (bebukele abo babetshiswa kuwo)
  85,7,Yaye baye baba ngamangqina oko babekwenza ngokuchasene nabakholwayo
  85,8,"Akukho tyala limbi ababelenzile (abakholwayo) ngaphandle kokukholwa kuAllâh, uSomandla, Ofanelwe ziindumiso zonke"
  85,9,Yena nguMnini bukumkani bamazulu nomhlaba! Yaye uAllâh UliNgqina ngaphezulu kwazo zonke izinto
  85,10,"(Inene abo batshutshisa amakholwa namakholwakazi ngokuwangcungcuthekisa) baze bangaguquki, baza kufumana isohlwayo sesiHogo, yaye baza kufumana isohlwayo soMlilo otshisayo"
  85,11,"Inene abo bakholwayo baze benze izenzo zobulungisa, okwabo iya kuba yiMiyezo ekumpompoza amanzi ngaphantsi kwayo. Leyo iya kuba yimpumelelo enkulu"
  85,12,"Inene\t(wena\tMuhammad)\tisohlwayo\tseNkosi\tyakho sibuhlungu kakhulu"
  85,13,"Inene\t(iNkosi\tyakho)\tyiYo\tEqalayo,\t(ukudala) Yiyo negqibelayo"
  85,14,"Yaye Yona nguMxoleli, uSoluthando"
  85,15,"UMnini Trone, eZukileyo"
  85,16,NguMenzi wentando yaKhe
  85,17,Ingaba ibali lemikhosi lifikile na kuwe
  85,18,(Imikhosi ) kaFir’awn namaThamûd
  85,19,Yeha abangakholwayo bayaqhubeka nokuphikisa (uMprofeti uMuhammad) nomyalezo wakhe oyi-Islam
  85,20,Kodwa Yena uAllâh Ubarhangqele ngemva kwabo
  85,21,Inene le yi’Kur’ân ezukileyo
  85,22,Ibhalwe eCwecweni elilondoloziweyo
  86,1,Ndifunga ngesibhakabhaka nangondwendwe lwasebusuku (inkwenkwezi ekhazimla kakhulu)
  86,2,"Yintoni\tna\tenokukucacisela\tokokuba\tundwendwe lwasebusuku yintoni na"
  86,3,Yinkwenkwezi ekukhazimla kwayo kugqobhozelayo
  86,4,Umphefumlo ngamnye unomkhuseli phezu kwawo
  86,5,Ngoko ke umntu makajonge ukuba udalwe ngantoni na
  86,6,Udalwe ngamanzi atsawulayo
  86,7,Avela phakathi komqolo neembambo
  86,8,Inene uAllâh Uyakwazi ukuphinda ambuyisele (ebomini) kwakhona
  86,9,NgeMini apho iimfihlelo ziya kuvavanywa
  86,10,Ngoko (umntu) akayi kuba namandla engayi kuba namncedisi
  86,11,Ndifunga ngesibhakabhaka (esiza nemvula) siphindaphinde
  86,12,Nangomhlaba ocazulukayo (xa kuhluma uhlaza kuwo)
  86,13,Inene le (‘Kur’ân) liLizwi elihluza (inyani ebuxokini)
  86,14,Yaye asiyonto yokonwabisa
  86,15,Inene bona baqulunqa iyelenqe ngawe (Muhammad)
  86,16,Kanti naM (oku kwaM) Ndiqulunqa icebo (ngokuchasene nabo)
  86,17,"Khawubayekelele abangakholwayo, ubaphathe ngobunono okwethutyana"
  87,1,"Zukisa igama leNkosi, UMlondolozi, Ophakamileyo"
  87,2,"Odale, Wacwangcisa ngokupheleleyo"
  87,3,"Owise (umthetho), Wanika isiKhokelo"
  87,4,Ovelise amadlelo aluhlaza
  87,5,"Aphinde awaguqule, Awenze atshazwe"
  87,6,Siyakukufundisawena(Muhammadi’Kur’ân) ngamanqanaba ukuze ungalibali
  87,7,Ngaphandle koko uAllâh Athande (ukuba ukulibale). Inene Yena Uyakwazi okubonakalayo nokungabonakaliyo
  87,8,Siya kukwenzela lula indlela yakho ukuze kube lula (ukushumayela i-Islam)
  87,9,Ngoko ke nika isilumkiso eluntwini kuba isilumkiso siluncedo
  87,10,Uya kusiphulaphula onoloyiko
  87,11,Kodwa asiyi kuhoywa ngonelishwa
  87,12,Yena lowo uya kungeniswa kuMlilokazi omkhulu
  87,13,Akayi kufa apho engayi kuphila
  87,14,Inene uyaphumelela ozihlambululayo
  87,15,"(Ohlala)\tekhumbula\tigama\tleNkosi\tyakhe\tathandaze nokuthandaza"
  87,16,Kodwa nina nikhetha ubomi beli hlabathi
  87,17,Nangona uBomi Obuzayo ibobona bulungileyo bungenaso nasiphelo
  87,18,Inene oku kukwiziBhalo zokuqala
  87,19,IziBhalo zikaIbrâhîm noMûsâ
  88,1,Ingaba iindaba zesiganeko (esikhulu) zifikile na kuwe
  88,2,"Ubuso babanye ngaloo Mini buya kudangala, (budane)"
  88,3,"Besebenze nzima, bediniwe. (ngenxa yokuzinikela kunqulo zithixo)"
  88,4,bangeniswe eMlilweni odwanguzayo
  88,5,Besezwa amanzi omthombo obilayo
  88,6,Akuyi kubakho kutya kwabo (apho) ngaphandle kwe- ‘Dhari’1 ekrakra
  88,7,"Engayi kubondla, ingayi kudambisa ndlala"
  88,8,Ubuso babanye ngaloo Mini buya kuchulumanca
  88,9,Bevuyiswa yimizamo yabo
  88,10,EMyezweni ophakamileyo
  88,11,Apho bangayi kuphinda beve ntetho inabungozi nabudenge
  88,12,Apho kuya kubakho umthombo ompompozayo
  88,13,Apho kuya kubakho iitrone eziphakamileyo
  88,14,Neendebe esele zilungisiwe kakade
  88,15,Neemandlalo (ezitofo-tofo) esele zidwelisiwe
  88,16,Neenkukho ezimfuma-mfuma sele zandlaliwe
  88,17,Abaziqwalaseli na iinkamela ukuba zidalwe kanjani
  88,18,Nesibhakabhaka ukuba siphakanyiswe kanjani na
  88,19,Neentaba (ezi) ukuba zimile (zaqina kanjani)
  88,20,Nomhlaba (lo) ukuba wandlalwe kanjani na
  88,21,"Bakhumbuze ke (Muhammad), inene wena ungumkhumbuzi"
  88,22,Awungomyaleli wabo
  88,23,Ngaphandle kwalowo ujibilikayo alahle ukholo
  88,24,Yena uAllâh Uya kumohlwaya ngesohlwayo esikhulu
  88,25,Inene kuThi kulapho baza kubuyela khona
  88,26,Kananjalo inene kukuThi apho baza kuphendula khona
  89,1,Ndifunga ngoms’obomvu
  89,2,Nangobusuku1 obulishumi
  89,3,Nangoku(dalwe) ngambini nangokungumnqakathi
  89,4,Nangobusuku xa busimka
  89,5,Ingaba kwezi (zifungo) zingentla apha akukho bungqina baneleyo na kubantu abanengqiqo (ukuba bashenxe kuzo zonke iintlobo zezono)
  89,6,Awubonanga na (Muhammad) ukuba iNkosi yakho Yenza njani na ngabantu bakwa’Ad
  89,7,Abakwa-Iram (ababebade kakhulu) ngathi ziintsika
  89,8,Ekungazanga kuphinde kudalwe abafana nabo ezweni
  89,9,Kanti namaThamûd ayeqhekeza amatye entlanjeni (akhe imizi yawo)
  89,10,Nabantu bakwaFir’awn umnini zibonda
  89,11,"Abagabadela, batsiba imida ehlabathini"
  89,12,Kulo apho benza ubutshinga obugqithisileyo
  89,13,Ngoko ke iNkosi yakho yathulula phezu kwabo iintlobo ngeentlobo zezohlwayo ezibuhlungu
  89,14,Inene iNkosi yakho Ihlala Ibajongile
  89,15,"Ke kaloku umntu, Ithi iNkosi yakhe Isakumvavanya ngokumnika intlonipheko nendyebo, asuke athi: (ngokuzigwagwisa): “INkosi yam Indinike intlonipheko.”"
  89,16,"Kodwa Ithi Yakumvavanya ngokuthi Imnciphisele isixhaso sakhe, (aqale) athi: “INkosi yam Indincitshile.”"
  89,17,Nakanye! Nina anizixabisanga iinkedama
  89,18,Yaye anikhuthazani ngokondla abasweleyo
  89,19,Yaye nidla amafa abo onke ngokunyoluka
  89,20,Kwaye nithanda ubutyebi ngothando olugqithisileyo
  89,21,Nakanye! Xa umhlaba ucunyuzwe wangumgubo
  89,22,"NeNkosi\tyakho\tIze\tneengelosi\t(zimi)\tngokwemiqolo ngemiqolo"
  89,23,"NesiHogo siya kuziswa kufutshane ngaloo Mini. Ngaloo Mini umntu uya kukhumbula, kodwa loo nkumbulo iya kumnceda ntoni"
  89,24,"Uya kuthi: “Kwowu! Akwaba ndandizenzele imisebenzi elungileyo kwangaphambili (ukusindisa) ubomi bam"
  89,25,Ke kaloku ngaloo Mini akukho mntu uya kohlwaya ngohlobo Aya kohlwaya ngalo Yena (uAllâh)
  89,26,Akukho mntu uya kuqamangela abenzi (bobubi ngohlobo) Aya kuqamangela ngalo Yena
  89,27,"(Kuya kuthiwa kumntu okholiweyo): “Wena ke mphefumlo osekuphumleni nasekwanelisekeni okupheleleyo"
  89,28,"Buyela eNkosini yakho ukholisekile, uYikholisile (naYo)"
  89,29,Ngena ngoko phakathi kwezicaka zaM
  89,30,Ngena ke ePaladesi yaM.”
  90,1,Ndifunga ngesi sixeko (saseMakkah)
  90,2,Wena (Muhammad) ungummi okhululekileyo wesi sixeko
  90,3,Nangomzali nangoko akuzeleyo
  90,4,Inene umntu Simdalele ekubulalekeni
  90,5,Ucinga ukuba akakho onamandla ngaphezu kwakhe
  90,6,"(Ude) athi (eqhayisa): “Ndichithe ubutyebi (bam) obuninzi!”"
  90,7,Ucinga ukuba akakho ombonayo na
  90,8,Asimenzelanga amehlo amabini na
  90,9,Nolwimi nemilebe emibini
  90,10,Sambonisa iindlela ezimbini (eliqhina nehlayo)
  90,11,"Kodwa akazamanga, ukalinyuka iqhina"
  90,12,Yintoni na enokukucacisela okokuba liyintoni na iqhina
  90,13,Kukukhulula ikhoboka
  90,14,Okanye ukondla (abantu) ngemini yendlala
  90,15,(Ukondla) inkedama esondeleyo (kuwe ngokuzalana)
  90,16,Okanye ihlwempu eliqhwanda uthuli. (ngenxa yentlupheko)
  90,17,Aze abe ngomnye wabo bakholwayo (kwi-Islam) abathi bakhuthazane ukunyamezela nomonde. Bakhuthazane kananjalo ngokuba nyulu nangokuba nemfesane
  90,18,Bona abo ngabo bangasekunene (abahlali basePaladesi)
  90,19,"Ke bona abo bangakholwayo kwiiVesi zeThu, (ze`Kur’ân) bona ngabo bangasekhohlo (abahlali basesiHogweni)"
  90,20,UMlilo uya kubagubungela
  91,1,Ndifunga ngelanga nangokumenyezela kwalo
  91,2,Nangenyanga xa ililandela
  91,3,Nangemini xa ibonisa ukukhazimla kwalo (ilanga)
  91,4,Nangobusuku xa buligquma
  91,5,Nangezulu nangaloWo Walakhayo
  91,6,Nangomhlaba nangaloWo Wawandlalayo
  91,7,Nangomphefulo nangaloWo Wawufezekisayo
  91,8,Waza kananjalo Wawubonisa okungawulungelanga noko kuwulungeleyo
  91,9,Inene uphumelele lowo uwuhlambululayo
  91,10,Akaphumelelanga lowo uwungcolisayo
  91,11,(Abantu) bakwaThamûd babaphikisa (abaProfeti babo) ngokugabadela kwabo
  91,12,Xa oyena mntu wayengcole kakhulu phakathi kwabo waphuma (waya kubulala imazi yenkamela)
  91,13,"Kodwa uMthunywa ka-Allâh (uSâlih) wathi kubo: “Ze nilumke! (Noyike isihelegu esiya kunihlela), yimazi yenkamela ka-Allâh le, ningayibulali okanye niyithintele ekuseleni amanzi wayo"
  91,14,"Bamphikisa ke bayibulala. Ngoko ke iNkosi yabo Yabatshabalalisa ngenxa yesono sabo, Yabenza batshabalala ngokulinganayo (abazizityebi nabangamahlwempu phakathi kwabo abangakholwayo)"
  91,15,Kwaye uAllâh Azanga Abe naloyiko lweziphumo zako oko
  92,1,Ndifunga ngobusuku xa bugubungela
  92,2,Nangemini xa ivela nokukhanya
  92,3,NangaloWo Wadala isiduna nesikhomokazi
  92,4,Inene imizamo nezenzo zenu zahlukahlukene
  92,5,"Lowo unikelayo (ngamalizo), esoyika uAllâh"
  92,6,Akholelwe kokulungileyo (kuAllâh)
  92,7,Inene Siya kumenzela mpuluswa indlela yokuhamba lula
  92,8,"Ke yena lowo unyolukileyo, uligogotya, ezicingela ukuba akaxhomekekanga ntweni"
  92,9,Aphikisane nokulungileyo
  92,10,Siya kumenzela mpuluswa indlela eya ekungcoleni
  92,11,Kanti buza kumnceda ntoni ubutyebi bakhe xa esiya entshabalalweni
  92,12,Inene kukuThi ukunika isiKhokelo
  92,13,Yaye inene seseThu isiphelo (uBomi oBuzayo) nesiqalo (ubomi beli hlabathi)
  92,14,"Ngoko\tke\tNdinilumkisile\tngoMlilo\todwanguzayo (wesiHogo)"
  92,15,Akukho mntu uza kungena kuwo ngaphandle kosisingcoli (owala ukukholwa kwi-Islam)
  92,16,"Ophikayo, atshikile"
  92,17,"Ke bona abamoyikayo uAllâh, baya kususwa babe kude kuwo (uMlilo)"
  92,18,"Lowo\tuchitha\tubutyebi\tbakhe\tekuzongezeleleni ukuhlambuluka komphefumlo wakhe"
  92,19,Ongenzeli (kunconywa) nakuhlawulwa ngumntu
  92,20,"Ngaphandle\tkokufuna\tukukholisa\tiNkosi\tyakhe Ephakamileyo, (uAllâh)"
  92,21,Kungekudala uya kwaneliseka (xa engeniswa ePaladesi)
  93,1,Ndifunga ngesandulela semini
  93,2,Nangobusuku xa bufiphala (buzolile)
  93,3,"INkosi\tyakho\t(Muhammad)\tAyikushiyanga,\t(futhi) Ayikuchasanga"
  93,4,Inene uBomi oBuzayo bobona bulungileyo kunobu (bomi balo mhlaba)
  93,5,Yaye inene iNkosi yakho Iya kukunika (konke okulungileyo) ukuze wena waneliseke
  93,6,"Yayingakufumananga uyinkedama na, Yakunika ukhuseleko"
  93,7,"Yakufumana kananjalo ulahlekile, Yakukhokela"
  93,8,Yakufumana ulihlwempu Yakwenza isityebi
  93,9,Ngoko ke ungayiphathi kakubi inkedama
  93,10,Ungaligxothi nengqiba
  93,11,Uvakalise uBabalo lweNkosi yakho
  94,1,Asikuvulelanga1 isifuba sakho na (Muhammad)
  94,2,Sakothulela umthwalo wakho
  94,3,Obukusinda umqolo
  94,4,Saza Saphakamisa ibakala lakho
  94,5,Inene kubo bonke ubunzima kukho ukukhululeka
  94,6,"Kanti, inene kubo bonke ubunzima kukho ukukhululeka"
  94,7,Ngoko ke wakugqiba (imisebenzi yakho yosuku) zinikele kunqulo luka-Allâh
  94,8,Yaye beka iingcinga zakho zonke eNkosini yakho
  95,1,Ndifunga ngomkhiwane nangomnquma
  95,2,Nangentaba yeSinayi
  95,3,Nangesi sixeko sokhuseleko (saseMakkah)
  95,4,Inene umntu Samdala ngesona simo silungileyo
  95,5,Saphinda Samthobisela kowona mgangatho uphantsi
  95,6,"Ngaphandle\tkwabo\tbakholwayo\tbenze\timisebenzi yobulungisa. Okwabo iya kuba ngumvuzo ongeze usilele"
  95,7,Yintoni ke emva koku enibangela ukuba niyiphike inkolo
  95,8,AyingoAllâh na Oyena Mgwebi Unobuluko kubagwebi
  96,1,Funda! Egameni leNkosi yakho Eyadalayo
  96,2,Yadala umntu ngehlwili legazi
  96,3,Funda iNkosi yakho Inesisa
  96,4,Yona Yafundisa ukubhala ngosiba
  96,5,Yamfundisa umntu oko abengakwazi
  96,6,Kodwa inene umntu uyagabadela
  96,7,Kuba uzicingela ukuba akaxhomekekanga ntweni
  96,8,Inene eNkosini yakho kulapho kuza kubuyelwa khona
  96,9,Umbonile na lowo uthintela
  96,10,Umkhonzi xa ethandaza
  96,11,Ingaba umbona ekuso isiKhokelo kusini na
  96,12,Okanye uyalela (abantu) ukuba bahlonele (uAllâh)
  96,13,"Umbonile na ukuba uphika inkolo, afulathele"
  96,14,Akazi na ukuba uAllâh Uyambona
  96,15,Nakanye ukuba akayeki siya kumrhuqa ngenwele zebunzi lakhe
  96,16,(Ezo) nwele zebunzi lexoki
  96,17,Makabize koogxabakhe (bamncede) ke
  96,18,Thina Siya kubiza abagcini siHogo. (Baqubisane naye)
  96,19,"Nakanye! Ungamthobeli lowo, wena, qubuda, uzisondeze (kuAllâh)"
  97,1,Inene esi siTyhilelo Sasityhila ngoBusuku baMandla
  97,2,Yintoni na enokukucacisela okokuba buyintoni na uBusuku baMandla
  97,3,UBusuku baMandla bungcono kuneenyanga eziliwaka
  97,4,"Ngabo kuhla iingelosi noMoya [oyiNgcwele (uJibrîl)] ngemvume ka-Allâh nemiyalelo yonke"
  97,5,(Ngobo busuku) kuba luxolo kude kube ngoms’obomvu
  98,1,Abo bangakholwayo phakathi kwaBantu beNcwadi nabanquli-zithixo babengekhe bayeke (ukuba ngabahedeni) de kwafika ubungqina obucacileyo kubo
  98,2,UMthunywa ovela kuAllâh ecengceleza iziBhalo eziNgcwele
  98,3,Apho kuzo kukho iiNcwadi ezilungileyo nezithe Tye
  98,4,Kananjalo aBantu beNcwadi babengezontlaba zahlukane de kwafika ubungqina obucacileyo
  98,5,"Ukanti babengayalelwanga nto yimbi ngaphandle kokukuba, banqule uAllâh, banyaniseke enkolweni yaKhe, banquleYena Yedwa, benze iSalâh (umthandazo), banikele ngeZakâh, oko ke yayiyeyona Nkolo ithe Tye"
  98,6,"Inene abo bangakholwayo phakathi kwaBantu beNcwadi nabanquli-zithixo baya kuba seMlilweni wesiHogo, ngonaphakade, bazezona zidalwa zibi"
  98,7,"Inene, ke bona abo bakholwayo, benza imisebenzi yobulungisa, bazezona zidalwa zilungileyo"
  98,8,"Umvuzo wabo oseNkosini yabo yiEdeni (uMyezo iPaladesi), ekumpompoza amanzi phantsi kwayo. Baya kuhlala apho kuyo ngonaphakade, uAllâh Uya kukholiseka ngabo nabo bakholiseke nguYe. Oko kokwabo bayoyikayo iNkosi yabo"
  99,1,Xa umhlaba uNyikima ngokunyikima kwawo
  99,2,"Uze\tutyekezele\tngaphandle\twonke\tumthwalo\twawo (obungaphakathi kuwo)"
  99,3,"Abantu baya kuthi: “kwenzeka ntoni na ngawo?”"
  99,4,Ngaloo Mini uya kuchaza iindaba zawo
  99,5,Kuba iNkosi yakho Iya kuwutyhilela (okwenzekayo phezu kwawo)
  99,6,"Ngaloo Mini abantu baya kuza bengamaqela athe saa, beze kuboniswa izenzo zabo"
  99,7,"Nabani\tna\tlowo\tuthe\twenza\tisenzo\tesilungileyo esingangentlantsi, uya kusibona"
  99,8,"Nalowo uthe wenza isenzo esingcolileyo esingangentlantsi, uya kusibona"
  100,1,"Ndifunga ngamahashe agabadula, akhefuzele"
  100,2,Atakise iintlantsi zomlilo (ngamanqina awo)
  100,3,Ephumelelisa uhlaselo lwawo kwasekuseni
  100,4,Aqhumise uthuli luye kutsho emafini kusenjalo
  100,5,"Agqobhoze, aye phambili angene esazulwini (sotshaba)"
  100,6,Inene umntu (ongakholwayo) akanambulelo eNkosini yakhe (uAllâh)
  100,7,Yaye inene ulingqina lako oko (ngezenzo zakhe)
  100,8,Kwaye inene unobutyhuthu-tyhuthu ekuthandeni kwakhe ubutyebi
  100,9,Akazi na okokuba xa okusemangcwabeni kuvunjululwe kwesaa ngaphandle
  100,10,Kuze noko kusezifubeni (zabantu) kwenziwe kwaziwe
  100,11,Inene iNkosi yakho ngaloo Mini Iya kuba Isazi konke ngabo
  101,1,(IYure) yesiThonga
  101,2,Yintoni na (iYure) yesiThonga
  101,3,Kananjalo yintoni na enokukuchazela okokuba iyintoni na iYure yesiThonga
  101,4,YiMini apho abantu baya kuthi saa njengamabhabhathane
  101,5,Iintaba zibe njengoboya obucazululweyo
  101,6,"Lowo\tuzenzo\tzakhe\tziya\tkufunyaniswa\tzinobunzima esikalini"
  101,7,Uya kuba sebomini obumnandi (ePaladesi)
  101,8,Ke lowo uzenzo zakhe ziya kufunyaniswa zilula esikalini
  101,9,Ikhaya lakhe liya kuba senzonzobileni (esiHogweni)
  101,10,Yintoni na enokukuchazela okokuba iyintoni na inzonzobila
  101,11,NguMlilo odwanguzayo
  102,1,Ukukhuphisana ngokuwanqa ubutyebi kuyaniphambukisa (ekukhonzeni uAllâh)
  102,2,Nide niye kubekwa emangcwabeni
  102,3,Yeha! Kungekudala niza kwazi
  102,4,Kwakhona yeha! Kungekudala niza kwazi
  102,5,"Yeha! Ukuba benisazi ngolwazi oluqinisekileyo (iziphumo zokuzilibazisa ngokuqokelela ubutyebi beniya kurhoxa kuloo nto, nizixakekise ngokukhonza uAllâh)"
  102,6,Inene niza kuwubona uMlilo odwanguzayo (wesiHogo)
  102,7,"Kwakhona, niya kuwubona ngamehlo okwenyani"
  102,8,"Kananjalo\tngaloo\tMini\tniza\tkubuzwa\tngobumnandi (enabuxhamlayo)"
  103,1,Nidfunga ngexesha
  103,2,Inene umntu usekulahlekeni
  103,3,"Ngaphandle kwabo bakholwayo, benza izenzo zobulungisa, bafundisane ngenyaniso, bafundisane nangomonde"
  104,1,Yeha kuye wonke (umntu) oyintlebi ohlebayo
  104,2,Oqokelele ubutyebi wabufumba
  104,3,"Ecinga\tukuba\tubutyebi\tbakhe\tbuza\tkumenza\taphile ngonaphakade"
  104,4,Nakanye! Uya kuphoswa koko kuqhawula (izinto) zibe zizicwibi
  104,5,Yintoni na enokukuchazela okokuba yintoni na eqhawula (izinto) zibe zizicwibi
  104,6,NguMlilo ka-Allâh osele uphenjiwe
  104,7,Olwatyuza uye kutsho ezintliziyweni
  104,8,Inene (uMlilo) uya kubagubungela
  104,9,uziintsika ezolulwe zande
  105,1,Awubonanga na ukuba iNkosi yakho Yenza njani na ngabanini ndlovu
  105,2,Ayizanga Ilenze liphanze na icebo labo
  105,3,Yathumela ibubu leentaka phezu kwabo
  105,4,Ezababetha ngamatye odongwe olutshisiweyo
  105,5,Yabenza banjengezala lentsimi elibhuqabhuqwe (ziinkomo)
  106,1,Ngenxa yolulanyiso lwama’Kuraysh
  106,2,Ekuwalulamiseni Senza iinqwelo zawo zorhwebo ziphume ebusika nasehlotyeni
  106,3,Ngoko ke makanqule iNkosi yalo Mzi
  106,4,"Ewondlileyo,\tYawasindisa\tendlaleni,\tYawakhusela naseloyikweni"
  107,1,Umbonile na lowo uphika inkolo
  107,2,Lowo ngulowo uphatha kakubi inkedama
  107,3,Ongakhuthazi kondliwa kwamahlwempu
  107,4,Yeha kubakhonzi
  107,5,Abangenankathalo ngemithandazo yabo
  107,6,Abanqwenela ukubonwa (ngabantu xa besenza izenzo zabo zonqulo)
  107,7,(Kodwa) besala namancedwana amancinane (eentswelo zobumelwane)
  108,1,Inene wena Sikuphe iKawthar
  108,2,"Ngoko ke thandaza eNkosini yakho, unikele (amadini) kuYo"
  108,3,Inene lowo ukuchasileyo nguye oza kunqanyulwa (angabikho alityalwe)
  109,1,"Yithi: Hini na nina bangakholwayo"
  109,2,Andikunquli oko nina nikunqulayo
  109,3,Nibe nani anikunquli oko mna ndikunqulayo
  109,4,Kanti nam andiyi kukunqula oko nina nikunqulayo
  109,5,Ukanti nani aniyi kukunqula oko mna ndikunqulayo
  109,6,Nina ninenkolo yenu nam ndinenkolo yam
  110,1,Lwakufika uNcedo luka-Allâh noloyiso
  110,2,Uze ubone abantu bengena enkolweni ka-Allâh (i-Islam) beziindimbane
  110,3,"Zukisa iNkosi yakho ke ngoko ngendumiso, ucele itarhu (kuYo). Inene Yona nguMxoleli Ohlala Esamkela inguquko"
  111,1,"Mazitshabalale zombini izandla zika-Abû Lahab, (naye) atshabalale"
  111,2,Ubutyebi bakhe nabantwana bakhe bungamncedi nganto
  111,3,Uza kutsha edangatyeni loMlilo odwanguzayo
  111,4,"Nomfazi wakhe, umthwalikazi weenkuni"
  111,5,Entanyeni yakhe uya kuqanyangelwa ngentambo yomthi wesundu
  112,1,"Yithi nguAllâh, Mnye (Jwi)"
  112,2,"UAllâh nguNaphakade, Uphelele"
  112,3,Akazali naYe Engazanga Wazalwa
  112,4,Ukanti akukho namnye ofana naYe
  113,1,"Yithi: Ndicela ukhuseleko ngeNkosi yoms’obomvu"
  113,2,Ekungcoleni kwezinto ezidaliweyo
  113,3,Ekungcoleni kobumnyama njengoko busanda
  113,4,Ekungcoleni kwabo benza ukuthakatha
  113,5,Nasekungcoleni kwalowo wenza umona njengoko esenza umona
  114,1,"Yithi: Ndicela ukhuseleko ngeNkosi yoluntu"
  114,2,UKumkani woluntu
  114,3,UThixo woluntu
  114,4,"Ekungcoleni\tkomsebezi\twokungcola\torhoxayo\t(emva kokusebeza) kwakhe"
  114,5,Lowo usebeza ezintliziyweni zoluntu
  114,6,Phakathi kweejinni naphakathi koluntu